thread.title_full: SecurCare Self Storage reviewed by Melissa A.

author: Melissa A.
title: Melissa A.
text: I've never heard of this company before and I was driving by so I decided to stop by because I know I'm going to be in need of storage within the next two weeks due to moving. The lady there, I believe her name was Lyric was great! She really knew what she was talking about. The property was nice and clean and so was the office and the have great prices and amanzing deals! I will be coming back to rent this week!
